",\n      \"优先补齐 JD 匹配缺口：核心技能：payroll、organizational skills；工具：quickbooks、cch axcess、proseries、lacerte；领域关键词：accounting、tax。\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"premiumMentors\": [\n    {\n      \"mentorId\": \"mentor_2_y導師\",\n      \"mentorName\": \"Y導師\",\n      \"company\": \"Amazon\",\n      \"companyLogo\": \"/logos/Amazon.png\",\n      \"mentorTitle\": \"Marketing Manager\",\n      \"badges\": [\n        \"现 Amazon\",\n        \"Marketing Manager\",\n        \"⭐ 高评分\"\n      ],\n      \"matchReason\": \"这位导师最匹配你当前的 JD 关键词和岗位匹配问题。\",\n      \"matchedProblems\": [\n        \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n        \"weak_summary_role_alignment\",\n        \"weak_target_role_alignment\",\n        \"partial_china_experience\",\n        \"low_hard_skill_match\"\n      ],\n      \"adviceItems\": [\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"7874a765-9b67-4382-bf02-3dcfc5658eff-2025-11-17-GAP分析和简历修改_chunk_009\",\n          \"title\": \"求职者在描述自主行业研究项目时陷入具体内容细节\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"简历与目标 JD 的关键词匹配偏低（当前约 27%），ATS 扫描时匹配信号不够强，容易在第一轮被过滤。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"将自主研究项目的简历描述重新定位：不讲报告内部具体结论，\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"没有服务过真实客户的自主项目，HR无法验证成果影响力，因此简历包装的落脚点应转移到研究方法与框架的专业性上，用结构化分析能力替代量化商业成果。\",\n          \"example\": \"修改前：描述电动商用车报告的具体内容（基础设施不足、AI趋势影响等）。修改后：'Independently developed a comprehensive industry research report on commercial EV sector, applying PESTLE framework to analyze regulatory trends, infrastructure gaps, and key market players; structured findings into actionable insights for potential investors/operators.'\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"项目没客户没数据，看你怎么包装能力\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"summary\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n            \"weak_summary_role_alignment\",\n            \"weak_target_role_alignment\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"db_adapted\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"7874a765-9b67-4382-bf02-3dcfc5658eff-2025-11-17-GAP分析和简历修改_chunk_012\",\n          \"title\": \"求职者记不清具体活动场次\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"目标岗位的核心技能词（如 payroll、organizational skills、quickbooks）在简历中出现不足，ATS 难以确认你的技能匹配度。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"当具体数字记不清时，\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"HR看到量化数字会对经历规模有直观感知，即使是保守估计也远胜于空白。使用「50+」「10+」等表达既符合事实又能有效传递工作量级。\",\n          \"example\": \"模糊表述：「参与拍摄多场学校活动」\\n量化表述：「Photographed and edited 50+ school events across 2 academic years」\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"有数字才能感受到工作量级\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"experience\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n            \"partial_china_experience\",\n            \"low_hard_skill_match\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"db_adapted\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"7a22ab6b-5d3f-4a2a-b475-004ada0e97bf-2025-10-25-MKT基础技能辅导和实习简历更新_chunk_010\",\n          \"title\": \"求职者因担心某些项目非自己独立完成而不敢写入简历\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"简历与目标 JD 的关键词匹配偏低（当前约 27%），ATS 扫描时匹配信号不够强，容易在第一轮被过滤。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"对于非自己主导的项目，以\\\"协助\\\"\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"\",\n          \"example\": \"改写前：（不敢写，因为赞助商对接是别人负责的）\\n改写后：「Assisted team in preparing pitch decks targeting both general audience and sponsors, supporting sponsorship acquisition efforts」\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"描述真实参与，不夸大，可信度高\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"experience\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n            \"partial_china_experience\",\n            \"low_hard_skill_match\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"db_adapted\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"mentorId\": \"mentor_1_u導師\",\n      \"mentorName\": \"U導師\",\n      \"company\": \"Morgan Stanley\",\n      \"companyLogo\": \"/logos/Morgan Stanley.png\",\n      \"mentorTitle\": \"Business / Risk Analytics  Senior Associate\",\n      \"badges\": [\n        \"现 Morgan Stanley\",\n        \"Business\",\n        \"前Intel\"\n      ],\n      \"matchReason\": \"这位导师最匹配你当前的 JD 关键词和岗位匹配问题。\",\n      \"matchedProblems\": [\n        \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n        \"low_hard_skill_match\",\n        \"weak_experience_keyword_evidence\",\n        \"partial_china_experience\"\n      ],\n      \"adviceItems\": [\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"7c127c7c-e0ea-4c50-aaf8-78a5bae326ac-2026-03-17-简历细节梳理(面试指导)_chunk_013\",\n          \"title\": \"求职者在描述项目时缺乏具体的行业背景设定\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"简历与目标 JD 的关键词匹配偏低（当前约 27%），ATS 扫描时匹配信号不够强，容易在第一轮被过滤。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"在简历项目描述中明确写出所处行业背景（如零售、供应链等），\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"项目描述若缺乏行业背景，HR只能得到框架性理解，无法感知候选人的实际业务能力。加入具体行业场景后，描述的可读性和说服力大幅提升。\",\n          \"example\": \"改前：「优化了公司资源配置，降低了运营成本」\\n改后：「在零售行业背景下，通过分析门店员工工资开支与采购花费，优化资源配置，降低运营成本X%」\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"场景不清楚，不知道他做的是哪个行业\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"experience\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n            \"low_hard_skill_match\",\n            \"weak_experience_keyword_evidence\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"db_adapted\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"7c127c7c-e0ea-4c50-aaf8-78a5bae326ac-2026-03-17-简历细节梳理(面试指导)_chunk_004\",\n          \"title\": \"求职者已有实习经历\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"目标岗位的核心技能词（如 payroll、organizational skills、quickbooks）在简历中出现不足，ATS 难以确认你的技能匹配度。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"将简历结构调整为：先展示当前及过往工作/实习经历，再列教育背景；\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"有工作经验的候选人应将工作经历置于教育背景之前，向HR传达「我已具备实战经验」的信号；同时针对JD中提到的技能，即使非正式工作经历习得，也应主动声明，让HR感受到你是「天选candidate」。\",\n          \"example\": \"简历结构调整示例：\\n【调整前】教育背景 → 实习经历 → 技能\\n【调整后】实习经历（当前） → 其他工作经历 → 教育背景（仅正式学历） → 技能\\n若JD要求Python但工作中未使用，可在技能栏注明「Python（自学，课外项目实践）」，补充与JD的关键词匹配。\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"经验放后面，重点不突出\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"experience\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n            \"partial_china_experience\",\n            \"low_hard_skill_match\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"db_adapted\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"7c127c7c-e0ea-4c50-aaf8-78a5bae326ac-2026-03-17-简历细节梳理(面试指导)_chunk_003\",\n          \"title\": \"不要一份简历投所有岗位\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"简历与目标 JD 的关键词匹配偏低（当前约 27%），ATS 扫描时匹配信号不够强，容易在第一轮被过滤。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"将简历结构调整为：工作/实习经历在前，教育背景在后。只有应届毕业生或无工作经验者才应将教育背景置顶。\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"HR查看简历时，结构顺序本身传递信息——工作经历置顶表明求职者以职业人身份定位自己；教育背景置顶则暗示经验不足，适合应届生而非有经验求职者。\",\n          \"example\": \"简历结构推荐顺序：1. 个人信息/Summary → 2. 工作/实习经历 → 3. 项目经历 → 4. 教育背景 → 5. 技能列表\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"有工作经历还把学历放第一，看起来像应届生\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"experience\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n            \"partial_china_experience\",\n            \"low_hard_skill_match\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"db_adapted\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"mentorId\": \"mentor_3_z導師\",\n      \"mentorName\": \"Z導師\",\n      \"company\": \"Morgan Stanley\",\n      \"companyLogo\": \"/logos/Morgan Stanley.png\",\n      \"mentorTitle\": \"FICC derivatives Asset management,VP\",\n      \"badges\": [\n        \"现 Morgan Stanley\",\n        \"FICC derivatives Asset managem\",\n        \"前Goldman Sachs\"\n      ],\n      \"matchReason\": \"这位导师最匹配你当前的 JD 关键词和岗位匹配问题。\",\n      \"matchedProblems\": [\n        \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n        \"low_hard_skill_match\",\n        \"weak_experience_keyword_evidence\",\n        \"partial_china_experience\"\n      ],\n      \"adviceItems\": [\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"78d56095-7e14-4924-8e77-b03afd5bc040-2025-01-17-GAP分析+简历修改-周鲲_chunk_008\",\n          \"title\": \"求职者的会计背景虽符合目标岗位要求\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"简历与目标 JD 的关键词匹配偏低（当前约 27%），ATS 扫描时匹配信号不够强，容易在第一轮被过滤。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"根据目标岗位类型，将对应关键词嵌入简历：risk岗位写入 value at risk、stress testing；\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"HR和hiring manager在筛选大量简历时，会对自身业务领域的专业关键词高度敏感。即使求职者背景匹配，若简历上看不到对应关键词，仍会在初筛阶段被过滤掉。关键词匹配是金融岗位简历通过初筛的必要条件。\",\n          \"example\": \"Risk岗位：在简历中写入 value at risk、stress testing；Product Controller岗位：写入 asset classes、portfolio、PNL、performance、P&L reconciliation；Treasury岗位：写入 financial forecasting、cash flow analysis。\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"关键词不够，不是我要的人\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"skills\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n            \"low_hard_skill_match\",\n            \"weak_experience_keyword_evidence\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"db_adapted\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"78d56095-7e14-4924-8e77-b03afd5bc040-2025-01-17-GAP分析+简历修改-周鲲_chunk_009\",\n          \"title\": \"求职者简历缺乏金融/银行岗位所需关键词\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"目标岗位的核心技能词（如 payroll、organizational skills、quickbooks）在简历中出现不足，ATS 难以确认你的技能匹配度。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"根据目标银行/金融岗位的JD，将相关关键词嵌入简历；\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"银行类岗位HR和ATS会重点扫描特定关键词（如财务分析、风控、合规等），简历若缺乏这些词汇，即使候选人有相关经验也难以被识别；工作经历丰富度直接影响HR对候选人的第一印象。\",\n          \"example\": \"\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"关键词不够，看不出金融背景\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"skills\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n            \"partial_china_experience\",\n            \"low_hard_skill_match\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"db_adapted\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"7c3406e3-a585-41ef-b2e5-ae2537eaf682-2025-07-12-求职方向定位&简历迭代思路沟通_chunk_027\",\n          \"title\": \"求职者目前只有单一版本简历\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"经历 bullet 中目标岗位的核心技能证据不足，技能更多出现在 Skills 栏，缺少在实际工作中使用它们的成果佐证。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"在开放申请时间节点后，出具多份针对不同职位的简历版本，分别投递对应岗位\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"一份简历打天下的策略命中率低，根据JD关键词定制不同版本简历，能有效提升ATS通过率和HR关注度\",\n          \"example\": \"\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"简历没贴岗位，直接跳过\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"overall\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n            \"low_hard_skill_match\",\n            \"weak_experience_keyword_evidence\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"db_adapted\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"mentorId\": \"fallback_mentor_4\",\n      \"mentorName\": \"V 导师\",\n      \"company\": \"Amazon\",\n      \"companyLogo\": \"/logos/Amazon.png\",\n      \"mentorTitle\": \"经历成果表达师\",\n      \"badges\": [\n        \"ATS 简历\",\n        \"导师知识库\"\n      ],\n      \"matchReason\": \"这位导师最匹配你当前的 JD 关键词和岗位匹配问题。\",\n      \"matchedProblems\": [\n        \"missing_exact_job_title\",\n        \"weak_summary_role_alignment\",\n        \"weak_target_role_alignment\",\n        \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n        \"low_hard_skill_match\",\n        \"weak_experience_keyword_evidence\"\n      ],\n      \"adviceItems\": [\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"fb_target_role_positioning\",\n          \"title\": \"先让简历看起来像 Accounting 岗位\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"你的简历目前有基础经历和教育背景，但和这份 JD 的岗位语言连接较弱。系统检测到 JD Match 和职位相关性都偏低，说明简历还没有稳定传达 Accounting 定位。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"先在 Summary 中自然加入 Accounting / Accountant 等目标岗位原词，并用一句话说明你与财务、报表、对账或审计支持相关的经验。\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"\",\n          \"example\": \"\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"summary\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"missing_exact_job_title\",\n            \"weak_summary_role_alignment\",\n            \"weak_target_role_alignment\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"fallback\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"fb_jd_keyword_alignment\",\n          \"title\": \"补上 JD 中真实掌握的 Accounting 关键词\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"当前简历缺少目标岗位会搜索的核心硬技能和工具词，导致 JD Match 分数偏低。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"把你真实掌握的 Accounting 相关关键词补进 Skills，例如 financial reporting、reconciliation、Excel、QuickBooks、GAAP、accounts payable/receivable、audit support 或 month-end close。\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"\",\n          \"example\": \"\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"skills\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"low_jd_keyword_match\",\n            \"missing_priority_keywords\",\n            \"low_hard_skill_match\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"fallback\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"adviceId\": \"fb_experience_keyword_evidence\",\n          \"title\": \"把关键词写进经历证据\",\n          \"problemSummary\": \"即使关键词出现在 Skills 区块，如果 Experience 中没有对应证据，ATS 和招聘方仍然难以判断你的真实匹配度。\",\n          \"actionSummary\": \"选择一段最相关经历，把 Accounting 关键词写进 bullet：说明你处理了什么报表、对账、发票或流程，并补充数量、频率或结果。\",\n          \"mentorInsight\": \"\",\n          \"example\": \"\",\n          \"hrPerspective\": \"\",\n          \"targetSection\": \"experience\",\n          \"relatedProblemTags\": [\n            \"weak_experience_keyword_evidence\",\n            \"keywords_only_in_skills\",\n            \"resume_not_tailored_to_jd\"\n          ],\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"source\": \"fallback\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-29T17:28:06.704Z\"\n}"}
